{"tid":163084,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Copy Cat出沒注意】買不到就要抄到足，Facebook Stories出爐","createTime":"2017-03-19T17:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T02:01:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3bd1372790707b7dcb985224ed66a7dde99acdb","tid":163084,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Facebook-Stories-FB-810x425.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FFacebook-Stories-FB-810x425.png&h=b2dc8e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFacebook近期動作全部都是「抄」！繼Facebook將Snapchat的限時故事功能「複製」至旗下社交平台，包括收購回來的Instagram和WhatsApp，以及自家開發的Messenger，近日再下一城，索性將這個功能也加入到「總部」Facebook上，「Facebook Stories」正式出爐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by TechCrunch<br />\n<br />\n不少人對Facebook Stories這項「新功能」都相當熟識，因為其與Snapchat的限時動態故事功能沒有分別。用家可以在照片上盡情塗鴉或加入貼圖，程式會將照片剪輯成短片，而張貼後24小時，短片便會自動消失。<br />\n<br />\n「Facebook Stories」推出後反應相當熱烈，雖然現階段只供愛爾蘭、智利、希臘及越南用戶試用，但相信很快便會拓展至全球用戶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by TechCrunch<br />\n<br />\n自從Facebook在2013年收購Snapchat失敗後，Mark Zuckerberg似乎心有不甘，陸續在旗下的社交平台上推出與Snapchat模式一模一樣的Story功能，即使被外界批評「毫無新意，只懂抄襲」，他亦繼續懶理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPhoto by The Information<br />\n<br />\n上市兩星期的Snap，當初在IPO建議書上亦將Facebook列明為主要風險因素，雖然上市首日股價大漲，但最近一星期卻一直徘徊在比開盤價還要低3美元的價位，明顯反映市場對Snapchat信心不足。"},{"pid":"4f66c8bc00e6cba63150aa98756bf34b4ce81353","tid":163084,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"反正Snapchat根本打唔入老年用家市場<br />\nFacebook個demographic其實好適合咁抄法<br />\n個learning curve又低，可以收窄generation gap"},{"pid":"60f9236724b2a39c6474956a8cf81dfe84bfeaa7","tid":163084,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b83d349355eb5e1d95fb69795e7c938fe4d6ea2","tid":163084,"uid":70962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:47:14.000Z","msg":"好無恥"},{"pid":"1a311a1f7ac64c6e139b8f342a0f10ff5cc445f9","tid":163084,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:22:38.000Z","msg":"你叫廢老玩story?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20c7a2f8fe4eba47a1c72a88429a460ff0c78cf","tid":163084,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"真係屌佢老仲未抄夠 同小米一鳩樣"},{"pid":"bef3bd04303563c38999d1a107d858e40c0aa475","tid":163084,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:24:00.000Z","msg":"祝佢全家身體健康"},{"pid":"ea046a30270a80bcd52ab03a44dc5d9a55715825","tid":163084,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a338364f91d217d065de3def38d526e5e411c91","tid":163084,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾facebook<br />\n搞完whatsapp啲用家都屌柒個垃圾function<br />\n而家facebook自己個app又搞多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過instagram抄完又完係好多人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}